    {
      "id": "1001893",
      "title": "",
      "description": "Here's what to know:\r\n\r\nWe have combined routes CT2 and 85 into the new Route 85, with service between Ruggles, Kendall/MIT, Spring Hill, Sullivan Square, and Assembly. The \u201cCT2\u201d route name will be retired.\r\n\r\nThese stops will no longer be served by Route 85:\r\nMain St @ Kendall Station - Red Line (Use the stop at Galileo Way @ Main St for outbound service)\r\nSomerville Ave @ Hawkins St (Use Rt 87 or Green Line instead)\r\nBow St @ Warren Ave (Use Rt 87 or Green Line instead)\r\n51 Bow St (Use Rt 87 or Green Line instead)\r\n\r\nAdditionally:\r\nService between Bow St and Spring Hill, which was paused for construction in 2023, will be discontinued permanently.",
      "severity": 1,
